ă basic.a+ ßßß Tiny BASIC Interpreter in A+ ßßß
ă
ă Line-numbered program storage, 26 variables A-Z, execution engine.
ă
ă Commands: LET X = expr, PRINT expr, IF cond THEN line#,
ă           GOTO line#, INPUT X, END
ă
ă Expressions: +, -, *, /, parentheses, variables, numbers
ă Conditions: =, <, >, <>, <=, >=
ă
